<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Mazard" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Mazard</orth> (the later Ff <emph>mazzard</emph>) the head, contemptuously: <cit><quote>knocked about the m. with a sexton's spade,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 5.1.97" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 1, 97</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I'll knock you o'er the m.</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 2.3.155" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 3, 155</bibl></cit>.
